<p>I have webapplication based on Spring, Java, JMS, JSP, on Weblogic server. On the Weblogic server I also have datasource which is used by my webapp.</p>  <p>1) Lets say JMS is configured as a foreign JMS server.  Some JMS message arrives. What decides that it must be distributed transaction? </p>  <p>2) Lets say JMS is configured on the same server as my webapp What kind of transation would start when a new JMS message arrives?</p>  <p>3) What and when decides which transaction type should be used?</p>